config VIDEO_HM2051
	tristate "HM2051 support"
	depends on I2C && VIDEO_V4L2 && VIDEO_XGOLD
	---help---
	This is a Video4Linux2 sensor-level driver for HM2051.

	iCatch is an external ISP connected to the sensor

	It currently only works with the atomisp driver.
